{"tid":1051093,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(G)I-DLE新歌只分配到幾句「嗚喔喔喔」 台灣成員舒華疑被排擠惹揣測","createTime":"2019-03-07T10:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T00:47:05.000Z","uid":9573,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5cf22e4df07debd074791f30d5c85aa616f8ce0a","tid":1051093,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"南韓女團「(G)I-DLE」出道時便狂掃各大音源排行榜，還奪下音樂節目NO.1，上月26日團體再推出新作品《Senorita》，但其中台灣成員舒華卻只分配到少少幾句，且都是「嗚喔喔喔」，引起大批粉絲不滿，3日晚間她在微博寫下長文吐露心聲，讓不少網友感到相當心疼，4日官方IG分享2張團體合照，舒華看起來相當疲憊也沒有笑容，再度引起網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/05/1809875-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F1809875-XXL.jpg&h=ef19c1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲年僅19歲的葉舒華，是繼子瑜後成功在南韓出道的女孩。<br />\n<br />\n舒華上次在3分44秒的新歌《Senorita》中，只有少少幾句，且都是「嗚喔喔喔」，令許多歌迷超傻眼，3日她在微博發文說道「回歸的這幾天，看到很多人給我的「建議」，我認為可以去做改變的我就會去改變、去學習，再更摸索自己，且保有自己的風格，謝謝那些真的為我好的人給我的留言，至於其他，我無感 擊敗不了我。」一番話讓人感到相當心疼，之後，4日官方IG分享的團體合照中，有眼尖的網友發現舒華看起來相當疲憊、完全零笑容，讓粉絲相當擔心她的身心狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/05/1809913-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F1809913-XXL.jpg&h=3dce5ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲舒華在微博吐心聲，也被發現官方團體照裡完全沒笑容。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/05/1809874-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F1809874-XXL.jpg&h=74bc8dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舒華在微博的貼文，引起許多粉絲關注，有不少人在底下留言鼓勵她，「加油阿，舒華！」粉絲也力挺她：「葉舒華是全世界最棒的小朋友，做你自己就好，我們會一直站在你的身後」、「超超超可愛的舒華，要好好照顧自己啊，不要看一些不好的言論你很棒。」官方曬出的「零笑容」團體照，也有不少網友前往留言打氣，並稱讚舒華很漂亮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/05/1809873-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F1809873-XXL.jpg&h=0024644a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲粉絲相當關心舒華的身心狀況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/53110850_1184860095028116_6932451517848879104_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=5f8bb5a117825362265c4f6d7376f01a&amp;oe=5D287B5A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F53110850_1184860095028116_6932451517848879104_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D5f8bb5a117825362265c4f6d7376f01a%26oe%3D5D287B5A&h=a6515cca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1529bcfdd3bf872fbefa91d63a049c032c87856","tid":1051093,"uid":129707,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T10:37:00.000Z","msg":"唱歌咁難聽點比歌詞佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47368b0dcc31bed0ef4993b71622b339d63c3bb","tid":1051093,"uid":192307,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"最尾個幅千雪係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b3e41b118e3bd9f17ceafe4cba3d0c6c5f094c","tid":1051093,"uid":192307,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e751179fd74df21e62d8680bee11014056ec73","tid":1051093,"uid":181527,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T12:35:16.000Z","msg":"佢之前唔係唱一句都炒車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d2c349a17f71a39a90b070b1046b5eaf23a709","tid":1051093,"uid":142787,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"佢大陸妹靚過佢又唱得好過佢"},{"pid":"dfa05544d18f1288af251113ced25a9557b6179f","tid":1051093,"uid":14437,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"f1d2c349a17f71a39a90b070b1046b5eaf23a709","tid":1051093,"uid":142787,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"佢大陸妹靚過佢又唱得好過佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyT